propList.Name: defaultOpenKeys
propList.Description: Array with the keys of default opened sub menus

propList.Description: custom expand icon of submenu

propList.Description: Specifies the collapsed status when menu is inline mode

propList.Description: Indent (in pixels) of inline menu items on each level

propList.Name: selectable

propList.Description: Style of the root node
